{{Infobox company| company_name = Audacious Inquiry | company_logo = [[File:Ai-logo-full.jpg|250px]] | industry = [[Health Information Technology]] | foundation = [[United States|USA]] (2004) | location = [[Baltimore]], [[Maryland]], [[United States|U.S.]] | num_employees = 115 employees (2017)| revenue = US $21.7 million (2017) | homepage = [http://www.ainq.com/ www.ainq.com] |
